        <name xml:lang="en">electricity, medium voltage</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kWh</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">A value of 0.0221 was reported by Kim and Overcash (2003). At the same time, a value of 0.044 kWh of electricity input was calculated based on data from an Indian plant (DSIR,1993). We, here, use the most conservative estimate of electricity input. 
References: 
